WEBVTT

00:00:01.182 --> 00:00:04.198
Raise your hand, and be honest,

00:00:04.222 --> 00:00:08.135
if you've used the phrase "crazy busy"

00:00:08.159 --> 00:00:13.273
to describe your day,
your week, your month.

00:00:14.441 --> 00:00:17.386
I'm an emergency-room doctor,

00:00:17.410 --> 00:00:22.390
and "crazy busy" is a phrase
you will never hear me use.

00:00:23.539 --> 00:00:25.459
And after today,

00:00:25.483 --> 00:00:28.340
I hope you'll stop using it, too.

00:00:29.166 --> 00:00:33.315
Here's why you cannot afford
to use "crazy"